Happy Friday everyone! Our new Production/Research intern, Jack Malsin, will be starting on Monday. You have seen/met Jack the last time he was in the office during the months of April and May. Jack will be joining us for the rest of the Summer to work on Sommely related tasks before he starts his Freshman year at Duke University! While young, Jack comes to us with an already stellar resume having co-founded a start-up named Peer Speak (<http://meyerhoffh.wix.com/peerspeak>) that provides a space for people to improve their language abilities through peer support and connection.  In addition to being interested in technology, Jack is very knowledgable in the realms of politics and current events and makes for a great conversation. When you have a few minutes, try and stop by and hi!
